smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f5cd0cd7be515d8cff2cb7b3cd9c8af3d61945f","tid":1911490,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T12:03:06.000Z","msg":"正常全世界貧民窟都係山上面<br />\n<br />\n想消滅支那，我們就要帶領支畜暴動和革命，才有機會從內部瓦解支共（輸出革命+加速主義，缺一不可）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1911527\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1911527</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n唔想香港淪為支那賤畜之境，大家必須肅清中資，整頓&ldquo;港漂&rdquo;<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1902243\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1902243</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n（國際戰線）借助日韓爆發武肺推動全球反奶共運動和全球排支運動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1894747\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1894747</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n中資禍港數十年，若不肅清，真香港人恐將不復存在<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1810669\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1810669</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n必須先紅後藍，否則中共恐成最後贏家<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1809175\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1809175</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"6c457a58a762545cc20b437b81fb89a7b1c170a6","tid":1911490,"uid":65024,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T12:42:05.000Z","msg":"我個賓賓都係咁講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2acdaf1238b895565938882dadd5e4df910b4f06","tid":1911490,"uid":298385,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T12:44:15.000Z","msg":"因為香港有維港"},{"pid":"3373be748fa23a6027a52384d5bf8b5cf065f854","tid":1911490,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T12:47:48.000Z","msg":"安達臣山都係窮鬼住。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f853fa5bbca0f924199109fb8a2b5b608bdaeed4","tid":1911490,"uid":107350,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T13:00:04.000Z","msg":"所謂香港既山上，半山，都係香港風水既龍脊位。<br />\n越住越旺，越住越富。<br />\n<br />\n（聽講係，除非唔係）"},{"pid":"7c4f2ca793765bca062001e1f5cdcd7d8728fce9","tid":1911490,"uid":110207,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T13:03:04.000Z","msg":"香港嚟講 <br />\n起碼二澳 西灣村嗰d先算山區"},{"pid":"ae7879de958c6f23bb0aee1bdab81aea14e7b9e5","tid":1911490,"uid":46849,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"71dd6fa0495bed4607b5cbfb1bf5688aaea9f1c4","tid":1911490,"uid":114360,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T11:03:28.000Z","msg":"香港根本冇山區<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T13:12:16.000Z","msg":"其實係<br />\n香港既所謂山區或偏遠地區<br />\n最多一小時就出到市區<br />\n而貴果d 根本渣車 15 分鐘就去到<br />\n<br />\n人地果d 山區<br />\n講緊渣車都要兩個鐘先出到去小鎮仲要得一間半間士多、油站、餐廳仔果d<br />\n兩個概念黎"},{"pid":"32f8113dddd2b3b193436a6768bbf5b2ea122509","tid":1911490,"uid":65024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ae7879de958c6f23bb0aee1bdab81aea14e7b9e5","tid":1911490,"uid":46849,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"71dd6fa0495bed4607b5cbfb1bf5688aaea9f1c4","tid":1911490,"uid":114360,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T11:03:28.000Z","msg":"香港根本冇山區<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T13:12:16.000Z","msg":"其實係<br />\n香港既所謂山區或偏遠地區<br />\n最多一小時就出到市區<br />\n而貴果d 根本渣車 15 分鐘就去到<br />\n<br />\n人地果d 山區<br />\n講緊渣車都要兩個鐘先出到去小鎮仲要得一間半間士多、油站、餐廳仔果d<br />\n兩個概念黎"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T13:3